Linux to Linux:

To generate SSH key:

#ssh-keygen

To copy ssh public key to other system:

#ssh-copy-id root@192.168.111.8

Windows to Linux:

	• Generate SSH Key by Putty Key-gen.
	• Now copy & paste public key to linux system.
	• Remove spaces after pasting into linux system.
		○ Press end button & then delete button.

	• Copy ssh public key to user OR root profile in following location

#vi /etc/root/.ssh/authorized_keys OR #vi /home/student/.ssh/authorized_keys